db.rstudio.com is a new website.

00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:22.000
It's talking about, like, we're trying to capture all the things

00:12:22.000 --> 00:12:25.000
that are related to sort of connecting from R to the database.

00:12:25.000 --> 00:12:29.000
spark.rstudio.com is the same kind of thing, but for Spark.

