there's an eval that you can download and run it,

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:42.000
but if you wanted to just play with it and see what the end user experience is like,

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:45.000
there's all the features, because it's a common shared infrastructure,

00:12:45.000 --> 00:12:47.000
but it'll give you a feel for, like, what you can publish,

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:49.000
how you can schedule, et cetera.

00:12:49.000 --> 00:12:51.000
So you can go to beta.rstudio.com and just log in with your Google Auth.

